        "result": "task_id: ses_361cb689effecVjeoYrwYHIIDd (for resuming to continue this task if needed)\n\n<task_result>\nNow I have a thorough understanding of the codebase. Here is the complete analysis:\n\n---\n\n# Super-Ralph Agent Framework â€” Full Codebase Analysis\n\n## 1. Directory Tree Overview\n\n```\nagent-framework/\nâ”śâ”€â”€ src/                          # All TypeScript source (19 files)\nâ”‚   â”śâ”€â”€ index.ts                  # CLI entry point â€” arg parsing & dispatch\nâ”‚   â”śâ”€â”€ engine.ts                 # Core Ralph loop (runPhaseLoop)\nâ”‚   â”śâ”€â”€ types.ts                  # Central type definitions\nâ”‚   â”śâ”€â”€ config.ts                 # Config loading & model resolution\nâ”‚   â”śâ”€â”€ events.ts                 # Event union type, pub/sub emitter, console renderer\nâ”‚   â”śâ”€â”€ run-state.ts              # Per-run artifact persistence (write)\nâ”‚   â”śâ”€â”€ run-status.ts             # Per-run artifact inspection (read-only)\nâ”‚   â”śâ”€â”€ progress.ts               # progress.md append/read\nâ”‚   â”śâ”€â”€ output-parser.ts          # SSE stream capture, 250K char buffer\nâ”‚   â”śâ”€â”€ timeout.ts                # Promise.race deadline utility\nâ”‚   â”śâ”€â”€ forward.ts                # Forward phase (beads â†’ code)\nâ”‚   â”śâ”€â”€ decompose.ts              # Decompose phase (spec â†’ beads)\nâ”‚   â”śâ”€â”€ reverse.ts                # Reverse phase (input â†’ spec)\nâ”‚   â”śâ”€â”€ init.ts                   # `super-ralph init` scaffolding\nâ”‚   â”śâ”€â”€ opencode.ts               # OpenCode server/session/SSE adapter\nâ”‚   â”śâ”€â”€ interactive.ts            # Interactive reverse: question handling via clack\nâ”‚   â”śâ”€â”€ beads.ts                  # `br` CLI adapter (spawns subprocesses)\nâ”‚   â”śâ”€â”€ skills.ts                 # Skill file resolution (built-in or path)\nâ”‚   â””â”€â”€ template.ts               # Handlebars .hbs template loader/renderer\nâ”‚\nâ”śâ”€â”€ templates/                    # Shipped project scaffolding templates\nâ”‚   â”śâ”€â”€ agents.md                 # AGENTS.md content for projects\nâ”‚   â”śâ”€â”€ forward.hbs               # Forward phase prompt template\nâ”‚   â”śâ”€â”€ decompose.hbs             # Decompose phase prompt template\nâ”‚   â”śâ”€â”€ reverse.hbs               # Reverse phase prompt template\nâ”‚   â”śâ”€â”€ intake-checklist.md       # Intake checklist\nâ”‚   â””â”€â”€ super-ralph-config.toml   # Default config template (copied on init)\nâ”‚\nâ”śâ”€â”€ skills/                       # Built-in skill question banks\nâ”‚   â”śâ”€â”€ feature.md\nâ”‚   â”śâ”€â”€ bug.md\nâ”‚   â”śâ”€â”€ hotfix.md\nâ”‚   â””â”€â”€ refactor.md\nâ”‚\nâ”śâ”€â”€ .opencode/                    # OpenCode plugin (installed per-project by init)\nâ”‚   â””â”€â”€ plugins/\nâ”‚       â””â”€â”€ super-ralph.js        # Registers `task_complete` tool in OpenCode\nâ”‚\nâ”śâ”€â”€ spec/                         # Reverse-engineered specifications\nâ”‚   â”śâ”€â”€ README.md                 # Purpose, scope, navigation, artifact table\nâ”‚   â”śâ”€â”€ CONVENTIONS.md            # Writing rules, confidence labels, template\nâ”‚   â”śâ”€â”€ module-catalog.md         # Inventory of all 19 modules by domain\nâ”‚   â”śâ”€â”€ architecture/\nâ”‚   â”‚   â”śâ”€â”€ overview.md           # Major domains, module boundaries, interactions\nâ”‚   â”‚   â””â”€â”€ runtime-lifecycle.md  # Init/loop/shutdown lifecycle detail\nâ”‚   â”śâ”€â”€ workflows/\nâ”‚   â”‚   â””â”€â”€ core-workflows.md     # 7 named workflows (WF-01 through WF-07)\nâ”‚   â””â”€â”€ modules/\nâ”‚       â”śâ”€â”€ cli/index.md\nâ”‚       â”śâ”€â”€ engine/engine.md\nâ”‚       â”śâ”€â”€ infrastructure/       # config, events, init, output-parser, progress,\nâ”‚       â”‚                         # run-state, run-status, skills, template, timeout, types\nâ”‚       â”śâ”€â”€ integrations/         # beads, interactive, opencode\nâ”‚       â””â”€â”€ phases/               # decompose, forward, reverse\nâ”‚\nâ”śâ”€â”€ docs